729032f-a.title: Richmond: Jewett Avenue - College Avenue
729032f-a.text:
806 Jewett Avenue, west side, between Collere Avenue and Shaw
Place, showing the old Purvis House (1898 to 1917 Sape). Earlier
(1874 map) it belonged to Mrs. M. Jewett.
April 2, 1924.
P.L. Sperr
